{"tid":549363,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"金正恩不甩制裁爽賺　北韓秘密基地傳是台灣","createTime":"2018-02-03T14:02:44.000Z","updateTime":"2018-02-04T08:34:27.000Z","uid":35790,"like":3,"dislike":7,"uniUserReply":40,"replies":[{"pid":"0e0cf7ed46ca33e3a71b3c5bd42ba5a468db6aec","tid":549363,"uid":35790,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-03T14:02:44.000Z","msg":"金正恩不甩制裁爽賺60億　北韓秘密基地驚傳是「台灣」<br />\n<br />\n2018-02-03 13:28<br />\n   <br />\n國際中心／綜合報導<br />\n<br />\n聯合國為制裁北韓，禁止北韓以出口煤礦等貨物賺取利益，但聯合國昨日公布的報告顯示，北韓去年仍透過出口礦產獲利近2億美元（約新台幣60億元）。對此，聯合國的監察團隊更查出，北韓偷運油的幕後「秘密基地」正是台灣，目前聯合國已盯上幾間油品公司，要來清查究竟是誰不甩禁令，仍違規偷賣油給北韓。<br />\n<br />\n聯合國針對北韓4艘貨櫃船下達禁令，不准它駛入全球任一港口，除了限制北韓出口煤炭、鐵、紡織品、海鮮等物，還不准他國販售石油給北韓。但台商陳世憲、莊錦宏先後被爆出偷賣油給北韓，嚴重違反聯合國安理會禁運決議，引起各界關注，也重創台灣形象。<br />\n<br />\n根據《CNBC》報導，聯合國昨日公布的報告指出，即便下達貿易禁令，但北韓仍在去年透過出口礦產及各類違禁品，獲利近2億美元。報告顯示，北韓利用偽造文件或其他規避手法，將出口的礦物偽裝成「他國產」，輸出至鄰近俄羅斯、南韓、中國大陸，甚至是馬來西亞、越南等國。<br />\n<br />\n另外，聯合國的監察團隊正著手調查，直指北韓偷運油的幕後基地正是台灣。至於還有多少商人違法，聯合國也已鎖定幾間跨國油品公司，要清查這些公司在與北韓交易的過程中，擔任什麼樣的角色，要予以懲罰。<br />\n<a href=\"http://www.setn.com/m/news.aspx?newsid=344572\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.setn.com%2Fm%2Fnews.aspx%3Fnewsid%3D344572&d=l1IC3F0VMvIjKG%2BDrtaQIxOFz4pMHIf1Ti9x7C0XgVU%3D&h=7140c92a\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.setn.com%2Fm%2Fnews.aspx%3Fnewsid%3D344572&h=acbaf2b3\" target=\"_blank\">http://www.setn.com/m/news.aspx?newsid=344572</a>"},{"pid":"164a6837ab01e15c36fef9682198c6e4a4c4fa4f","tid":549363,"uid":61653,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-03T14:05:09.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"56d2e82fa6dc4a2f13f38eb590844ec9ad724b6a","tid":549363,"uid":35790,"like":136,"dislike":1,"score":135,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-03T14:05:21.000Z","msg":"台灣又不是聯合國的成員<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ae398970213bd37517755230f17c5b1eedd4d03c","tid":549363,"uid":1781,"like":7,"dislike":6,"score":1,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-02-03T14:05:29.000Z","msg":"台灣冇加入到聯合國<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"42e2bbff55c10e2c07e0f4c84b77e86f67ac28fa","tid":549363,"uid":34409,"like":77,"dislike":1,"score":76,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-02-03T14:07:12.000Z","msg":"聯合國你唔係將台灣歸為中國既咩？<br />\n你咪去搵中國算賬囉~<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b97b90423a60591cd227ccd46f6bc56b7feb4467","tid":549363,"uid":53026,"like":92,"dislike":1,"score":91,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-03T14:07:27.000Z","msg":"你聯合國踢走台灣，咁點解要人聽你支笛？"},{"pid":"3671bdb39f994791e553e51393255281b99c5bfd","tid":549363,"uid":35790,"like":22,"dislike":1,"score":21,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-03T14:08:34.000Z","msg":"台灣人用台護照入唔到聯合國大廈參觀"},{"pid":"e135bcd12d5ee981c79b084d04ce924f905c6b69","tid":549363,"uid":57394,"like":11,"dislike":0,"score":11,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-03T14:08:43.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"eddc57a3d8c9acf57efb5b99727b011481af8351","tid":549363,"uid":33643,"like":2,"dislike":7,"score":-5,"quote":{"pid":"ae398970213bd37517755230f17c5b1eedd4d03c","tid":549363,"uid":1781,"like":7,"dislike":6,"score":1,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-02-03T14:05:29.000Z","msg":"台灣冇加入到聯合國<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-02-03T14:08:50.000Z","msg":"自己google下先好問啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5116108bdf4cd895e5b8d46e9e432313d99abc64","tid":549363,"uid":35790,"like":33,"dislike":0,"score":33,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-02-03T14:12:58.000Z","msg":"中國話台灣係中國領土-中國台灣省<br />\n中國理應負責監督台灣省遵守聯合國決議<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"687555c3fccc87d7f11c1750253dce854afa51a6","tid":549363,"uid":33643,"like":16,"dislike":0,"score":16,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-03T14:14:42.000Z","msg":"呢單嘢衍生到好多外交問題<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6ad455131d52eb2eb1bd5f91fa8881e74017b349","tid":549363,"uid":50457,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-03T14:16:32.000Z","msg":"台灣同聯合國有咩關係？<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7feff7c41359682b9e9acfb5da1b4b912f36097c","tid":549363,"uid":4783,"like":18,"dislike":0,"score":18,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-03T14:19:18.000Z","msg":"台灣人都唔俾入un總部參觀架，咁台灣既詳細問題，我覺得un可以返去問中國<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"26a53db5c91fdc27137c2b6866bf5e3410b1a6fc","tid":549363,"uid":50457,"like":12,"dislike":1,"score":11,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-03T14:19:20.000Z","msg":"中國唔係堅持九二共識既咩，呢次大大方方認咗佢大家未信你有信用囉<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/06.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ba81f11c6b2abde9419118311a835eba9f5d9817","tid":549363,"uid":31219,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-03T14:20:17.000Z","msg":"返去鬧中國囉<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/06.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3a0d07520dcd5c586a163c7c766398619d0b6b68","tid":549363,"uid":12757,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"ae398970213bd37517755230f17c5b1eedd4d03c","tid":549363,"uid":1781,"like":7,"dislike":6,"score":1,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-02-03T14:05:29.000Z","msg":"台灣冇加入到聯合國<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-02-03T14:21:15.000Z","msg":"當初開羅宣言係台灣<br />\n但之後支那加入聯合國 台灣抗議而退出<br />\n<br />\n咁支那就冇機會成為常任國"},{"pid":"968b38df5d20962d3ce23b4c436f2c54b637c0b0","tid":549363,"uid":35790,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"quote":{"pid":"5116108bdf4cd895e5b8d46e9e432313d99abc64","tid":549363,"uid":35790,"like":33,"dislike":0,"score":33,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-02-03T14:12:58.000Z","msg":"中國話台灣係中國領土-中國台灣省<br />\n中國理應負責監督台灣省遵守聯合國決議<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-02-03T14:22:18.000Z","msg":"海運駁油給北韓  聯合國報告：主要來源是中國台灣省<br />\n<br />\n〔即時新聞／綜合報導〕北韓因發展核武遭聯合國實施一連串制裁，但聯合國調查指出，即便如此，北韓仍偷來暗去賺進約2億美元（約台幣58億），且還特別點出，台灣是透過海運運送原油給北韓的主要來源。<br />\n<br />\n根據《路透》報導，北韓利用偽造文件，將自家煤炭偽裝成他國出產，並售往俄羅斯、中國、南韓、等國，另外還分別向敘利亞、緬甸輸出武器，在去年入帳58億元台幣。<br />\n<br />\n聯合國調查員還特別指出，透過海運送油給北韓的違規船隻，主要來源都是台灣，且報導中還強調是「中國台灣省」，有多間跨國油品公司，已經被聯合國鎖定並調查，以釐清他們在偷賣給北韓過程中的角色，至於是哪幾家公司，報告並未詳列。<br />\n<br />\n台灣商人陳世憲所有的「方向永嘉號」，先前遭抓包駁油給北韓；近日又有一名漁界商人莊錦宏所持有的「金穗輪」被美國人造衛星拍到，在東海公海駁油北韓牟利。<br />\n<a href=\"http://m.ltn.com.tw/news/world/breakingnews/2331470\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fm.ltn.com.tw%2Fnews%2Fworld%2Fbreakingnews%2F2331470&d=l1IC3F0VMvIjKG%2BDrtaQIxOFz4pMHIf1Ti9x7C0XgVU%3D&h=f91fe7be\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fm.ltn.com.tw%2Fnews%2Fworld%2Fbreakingnews%2F2331470&h=09bf2082\" target=\"_blank\">http://m.ltn.com.tw/news/world/breakingnews/2331470</a><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7bdc29eedeebfa836ff2f46759ec62ac8cce3e46","tid":549363,"uid":123711,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-02-03T14:26:04.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"f6dd9e64ffa77a2d6df77d70edc01b41c5b85c3b","tid":549363,"uid":35790,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"7bdc29eedeebfa836ff2f46759ec62ac8cce3e46","tid":549363,"uid":123711,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"968b38df5d20962d3ce23b4c436f2c54b637c0b0","tid":549363,"uid":35790,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"quote":{"pid":"5116108bdf4cd895e5b8d46e9e432313d99abc64","tid":549363,"uid":35790,"like":33,"dislike":0,"score":33,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-02-03T14:12:58.000Z","msg":"中國話台灣係中國領土-中國台灣省<br />\n中國理應負責監督台灣省遵守聯合國決議<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-02-03T14:22:18.000Z","msg":"海運駁油給北韓  聯合國報告：主要來源是中國台灣省<br />\n<br />\n〔即時新聞／綜合報導〕北韓因發展核武遭聯合國實施一連串制裁，但聯合國調查指出，即便如此，北韓仍偷來暗去賺進約2億美元（約台幣58億），且還特別點出，台灣是透過海運運送原油給北韓的主要來源。<br />\n<br />\n根據《路透》報導，北韓利用偽造文件，將自家煤炭偽裝成他國出產，並售往俄羅斯、中國、南韓、等國，另外還分別向敘利亞、緬甸輸出武器，在去年入帳58億元台幣。<br />\n<br />\n聯合國調查員還特別指出，透過海運送油給北韓的違規船隻，主要來源都是台灣，且報導中還強調是「中國台灣省」，有多間跨國油品公司，已經被聯合國鎖定並調查，以釐清他們在偷賣給北韓過程中的角色，至於是哪幾家公司，報告並未詳列。<br />\n<br />\n台灣商人陳世憲所有的「方向永嘉號」，先前遭抓包駁油給北韓；近日又有一名漁界商人莊錦宏所持有的「金穗輪」被美國人造衛星拍到，在東海公海駁油北韓牟利。<br />\n<a href=\"http://m.ltn.com.tw/news/world/breakingnews/2331470\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fm.ltn.com.tw%2Fnews%2Fworld%2Fbreakingnews%2F2331470&d=l1IC3F0VMvIjKG%2BDrtaQIxOFz4pMHIf1Ti9x7C0XgVU%3D&h=f91fe7be\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fm.ltn.com.tw%2Fnews%2Fworld%2Fbreakingnews%2F2331470&h=09bf2082\" target=\"_blank\">http://m.ltn.com.tw/news/world/breakingnews/2331470</a><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-02-03T14:26:04.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-03T14:29:07.000Z","msg":"聯合國調查員係咩國籍？"},{"pid":"3f90912d69252f79e98652a8cdd46bb4202e95a8","tid":549363,"uid":62226,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-03T14:29:13.000Z","msg":"台灣使唔使守聯合國禁令？"},{"pid":"f9a49d32b5f1b6f6d2f28cc409f30a07018f3210","tid":549363,"uid":59898,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-03T14:32:06.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"13fe757f03b5b0894d7125ce630e023a160071c8","tid":549363,"uid":4564,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"3a0d07520dcd5c586a163c7c766398619d0b6b68","tid":549363,"uid":12757,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"ae398970213bd37517755230f17c5b1eedd4d03c","tid":549363,"uid":1781,"like":7,"dislike":6,"score":1,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-02-03T14:05:29.00